snippet.title: Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2011 (PS3) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2011, a baseball video game by Konami for PlayStation 3. Yakult Swallows vs. Chunichi Dragons at the neighborhood park.
